      *                                           riferimento          *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-p1i : 1. periodo data min  *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-p1f : 1. periodo data max  *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-p2i : 2. periodo data min  *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-p2f : 2. periodo data max  *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-p3i : 3. periodo data min  *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-p3f : 3. periodo data max  *
      *                                                                *
      *                       rf-fit            : Non significativo    *
      *                                                                *
      *                       rf-fir            : Non significativo    *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      *              Output : nessuno                                  *
      *                                                                *
      *       -------------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * "GT"  Lettura sequenziale archivio [fit]                       *
      *                                                                *
      *              Input  : w-mod-fat-fit-ope : "GT"                 *
      *                                                                *
      *                       rf-fit            : Non significativo    *
      *                                                                *
      *                       rf-fir            : Non significativo    *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      *              Output : rf-fit            : Record [fit] ottenu- *
      *                                           to                   *
      *                                                                *
      *                       rf-fir            : Non significativo    *
      *                                                                *
      *                       w-mod-fat-fit-flg : Si/No fine file      *
      *                                             - Spaces : No      *
